While stressing the need for the education sector shifting focus from knowledge accumulation to skill development, Prasad B. Roodagi, director of KLESâ€™ Institute of Management Studies and Research, suggested introducing Digital Class Theatre (DCT) in tier 2 cities. In his presentation at a pre-budget consultative meeting convened by Pralhad Joshi, MP, here on Sunday, Mr. Roodagi said that DCT would revolutionise the education sector by facilitating access to the global knowledge bank for students and teachers.